name: Bunny-girl with Golden tummy
description:
What could be cuter than a girl bunny? That's right! A girl bunny with a golden tummy! Our bunny loves to serve customers, she is just waiting to be asked to make a cocktail or dance. Don't keep her waiting and ask for something too! ♡

Easy win: Keyboard Сtrl+D - Complete Level

FEATURES

  • ⭐ Beautiful artwork
  • ⭐ Animation scenes
  • ⭐ Relaxing music
  • ⭐ CG Gallery Mode
  • ⭐ Puzzle game
